task.summary: Default task
Gave MerkleTreeBuilder a setHash()-Method.
Fixed createNodeStructure(); was complete nonsense before
Commented a bunch of stuff
Modified search() and setValue() to throw exceptions when needed.
Now calculatePathToNode() throws an IndexOutOfBoundsException; search itself not anymore
fixed bug in push() (was expanding too often) by changing the update()-Method for MerkleInnerNode not to set a hash when at least one of the children doesn't have a hash.
Fixed bug in calculateHash() in MerkleLeaf
Implemented hashCode in class Body.
Started Shell-implementation.
Shell should be about done.
Fixed bug where calling certain commands before NEW would crash the program
Fixed toString().
Changed Mode-definitions from boolean to int which is more secure due to int not having a default value, unlike boolean.
Implemented getMissing() in MutableMerkleTree and MerkleInnerNode and MerkleLeaf and adjustet Shell to work with it properly.
implemented getMissing() and adjusted Shell accordingly
changed setValue() in MutableMerkleTree to take a leaf-index as an argument, rather than a BFS-index.
Adjusted tree to not accept size-values < 2 and adjusted shell to never update the root-hash in check-mode
created deafult-constructor for MutableMerkleTree that just throws an exception
check-command now only works when tree is ready
when checking a tree, root now always needs to be verified (e.g. [1,2] are now missing when only root is present)
fixed bugs in handleCheck and getMissing()
fixed bug where Cylinder had Cuboid(x,y,z) as toString()-value
scanner now gets closed when the program quits
when passing nothing as a command (ctrl+D) now the program terminates
the scanner now gets closed after every command
shell now checks if there are too many arguments for a given command
wrote help-messages
implemented UnmodifiableMerkleTree as a wrapper for MutableMerkleTree
changed build() in MerkleTreeBuilder to return an UnmodifiableMerkleTreee
made toIndexString() in shell simpler and easier to read by replacing the for-loop with a replaceAll-operation
purged magic number from getStoredHash()
made the detection of being in the wrong mode exception-based
Edited and added some comments
created new package for Body, Cuboid and Cylinder
Reformatted code
fixed toString() in Cuboid and Cylinder
got rid of Bodies-package
formatted stuff
more formatting
more more formatting
Modified toString() in MerkleLeaf to display the hash when there is no value (Body-object) present.
fixed bug where isConsistend would cause a NoSuchElementException
fixed bug where isConsistend would cause a NullPointerException
completely re-implemented isConsistent to avoid all exceptions
completely re-implemented isConsistent to avoid all exceptions (again)
fixed bug where set_val would override the root-hash
added bodies-package and comments
